### 函数传参

类似python的两种方法，一是按照函数定义的顺序直接填入，二是通过花括号指定传入哪个形参，如下例：

```solidity
pragma solidity ^0.4.16;

contract parma{
    uint public num;
    string public name;
    function setParam(uint _num,string _name){
        num=_num;
        name=_name;
    }
    function T1(){
        setParam(18,"J1an");
    }
    function T2(){
        setParam({_name:"Ben",_num:20});
